               <p>Did you ever tell Rowley and Ambler, to swear plump against him, or else he would not be fully committed? - Never, I did not know the gentlemen, till they came to find the bill last Friday week.</p>
               <p>Did you ever tell any body, to swear plump against him, or any thing to that purpose? - Never, nor any thing to that purpose.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. Do not you remember lifting up your hand in our three faces, and saying that if ever a one of us spoke a word for him, he would perjure us all three? - No, never, I saw none but the mother.</p>
